by stof at 2021-11-09T11:08:53Z

To me, this kind of discovery is better handled using keywords than using the type (which has a single value).

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

by nicolas-grekas at 2021-11-09T11:12:44Z

Updating the type still makes sense to me: e.g. `symfony-messenger-bridge` is a better type description than `symfony-bridge` to me.

