by GromNaN at 2021-11-09T11:34:31Z

On packagist there is a filter on tags, not on type. How would you search a package on its type?

https://packagist.org/?query=symfony-bridge does not return symfony packages.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

by nicolas-grekas at 2021-11-09T11:35:31Z

https://packagist.org/?type=symfony-bridge

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

by stof at 2021-11-09T11:35:44Z

@GromNaN packagist has both a filter by type and by tags (packagist's name for keywords). But the `query` parameter is about searching by name.
